VM Setup Process

0. Setup discard, etc
1. Start with stock Ubuntu 14.04.3 (btrfs-based install)
2a. Run all updates
2b. Install dkms + guest additions (from CD)
3. Add cu-cs-apt package
4. Install cu-cs-vm-<flavor> package
5. Run update, autoremove, clean
6. Tweak Terminal Color Settings -> Tango
7a. Set default launcher/desktop icons + background
7b. Disable screen lock, screensaver, etc
8. Check Dropbox
9. Clear History
10. Create btrfs read-only snapshots
11. Reboot
12. Shutdown
13. Image
